Package: koopman.dmd
Type: Package
Title: Koopman Operator and Dynamic Mode Decomposition for Dynamical Systems
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("James", "Harris", email = "jimeharrisjr@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Dynamic Mode Decomposition (DMD) with Koopman operator theory extensions,
    powered by a Rust backend via extendr. Includes standard DMD, Extended DMD with
    lifting functions, Hankel-DMD, Generalized Laplace Analysis (GLA), harmonic time
    averages, and mesochronic harmonic plots for phase space analysis.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
SystemRequirements: Cargo (Rust's package manager), rustc
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: stats, graphics, grDevices
Suggests: testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/rextendr/version: 0.3.1
